data.description: Wonderful 2 story townhome in the heart of Lake Wylie/Clover. This 3-bedroom 2.5 bath home is located in the gated community of Harper’s Green subdivision features a spacious, open floorplan. The main level boasts a large living area open to the kitchen, a drop zone, breakfast area, and a dining room that can be used as a preferred office. The patio overlooks a fenced in back yard great for grilling and entertaining. Upstairs there is a loft style bonus room, primary bedroom with en suite, two more bedrooms and a full bath. Location is perfect minutes from Charlotte border and close to shopping, dining, and all Lake Wylie has to offer. Seller is a nurse and have puppies which makes showing appointments difficult. Please call listing agent for showings.
